Custom embedded hardware project built from concept to prototype. Designed and fabricated 
flexible and rigid PCBs for embedding in a dental retainer, including a custom power 
management board with wireless charging.

Integrated multimodal sensing — flexible resistive sensors, bone conduction microphones, 
IMU, thermocouple, and pulse oximetry. Developed firmware on Zephyr RTOS for Nordic 
nRF52/nRF53 with BLE data streaming, OTA update capability, and NOR flash memory management.
Built a reflow oven and hand-assembled micro-scale PCBs with SMD components.